short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Companion app for RaceTab Meet Manager 4 to receive late entries for a meet. Talks directly with RaceTab on the Windows PC.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This application works with RaceTab Meet Manager, running on a Windows PC, and allows you to have another work station on the local wireless network where staff can register new atheltes.
